[
  {
    "text": "Today I stand before you\nas a man who lives life to the full",
    "start": 12.76,
    "duration": 4.016
  },
  {
    "text": "in the here and now.",
    "start": 16.8,
    "duration": 1.24
  },
  {
    "text": "But for a long time,",
    "start": 19.28,
    "duration": 1.656
  },
  {
    "text": "I lived for death.",
    "start": 20.96,
    "duration": 1.2
  },
  {
    "text": "I was a young man who believed",
    "start": 23.92,
    "duration": 1.616
  },
  {
    "text": "that jihad is to be understood\nin the language of force and violence.",
    "start": 25.56,
    "duration": 4.56
  },
  {
    "text": "I tried to right wrongs\nthrough power and aggression.",
    "start": 32.76,
    "duration": 3.24
  },
  {
    "text": "I had deep concerns\nfor the suffering of others",
    "start": 37.44,
    "duration": 4.44
  },
  {
    "text": "and a strong desire\nto help and bring relief to them.",
    "start": 42.76,
    "duration": 3.24
  },
  {
    "text": "I thought violent jihad was noble,",
    "start": 49.12,
    "duration": 3.336
  },
  {
    "text": "chivalrous",
    "start": 52.48,
    "duration": 1.336
  },
  {
    "text": "and the best way to help.",
    "start": 53.84,
    "duration": 1.32
  },
  {
    "text": "At a time when so many of our people --",
    "start": 57.64,
    "duration": 1.896
  },
  {
    "text": "young people especially --",
    "start": 59.56,
    "duration": 1.256
  },
  {
    "text": "are at risk of radicalization",
    "start": 60.84,
    "duration": 1.56
  },
  {
    "text": "through groups like al-Qaeda,",
    "start": 63.4,
    "duration": 1.696
  },
  {
    "text": "Islamic State and others,",
    "start": 65.12,
    "duration": 1.84
  },
  {
    "text": "when these groups are claiming",
    "start": 67.88,
    "duration": 1.456
  },
  {
    "text": "that their horrific brutality\nand violence are true jihad,",
    "start": 69.36,
    "duration": 5.056
  },
  {
    "text": "I want to say that their idea\nof jihad is wrong --",
    "start": 74.44,
    "duration": 4.176
  },
  {
    "text": "completely wrong --",
    "start": 78.64,
    "duration": 1.336
  },
  {
    "text": "as was mine, then.",
    "start": 80.0,
    "duration": 1.2
  },
  {
    "text": "Jihad means to strive to one's utmost.",
    "start": 83.2,
    "duration": 2.36
  },
  {
    "text": "It includes exertion and spirituality,",
    "start": 86.44,
    "duration": 3.016
  },
  {
    "text": "self-purification",
    "start": 89.48,
    "duration": 1.496
  },
  {
    "text": "and devotion.",
    "start": 91.0,
    "duration": 1.2
  },
  {
    "text": "It refers to positive transformation",
    "start": 94.48,
    "duration": 2.776
  },
  {
    "text": "through learning, wisdom\nand remembrance of God.",
    "start": 97.28,
    "duration": 4.096
  },
  {
    "text": "The word jihad stands\nfor all those meanings as a whole.",
    "start": 101.4,
    "duration": 3.24
  },
  {
    "text": "Jihad may at times\ntake the form of fighting,",
    "start": 106.92,
    "duration": 4.416
  },
  {
    "text": "but only sometimes,",
    "start": 111.36,
    "duration": 1.2
  },
  {
    "text": "under strict conditions,",
    "start": 113.2,
    "duration": 1.72
  },
  {
    "text": "within rules and limits.",
    "start": 116.2,
    "duration": 1.96
  },
  {
    "text": "In Islam,",
    "start": 119.84,
    "duration": 1.216
  },
  {
    "text": "the benefit of an act must outweigh\nthe harm or hardship it entails.",
    "start": 121.08,
    "duration": 5.0
  },
  {
    "text": "More importantly,",
    "start": 127.24,
    "duration": 1.736
  },
  {
    "text": "the verses in the Koran\nthat are connected to jihad or fighting",
    "start": 129.0,
    "duration": 4.736
  },
  {
    "text": "do not cancel out the verses\nthat talk about forgiveness,",
    "start": 133.76,
    "duration": 5.576
  },
  {
    "text": "benevolence",
    "start": 139.36,
    "duration": 1.296
  },
  {
    "text": "or patience.",
    "start": 140.68,
    "duration": 1.2
  },
  {
    "text": "But now I believe that there are\nno circumstances on earth",
    "start": 145.32,
    "duration": 4.576
  },
  {
    "text": "where violent jihad is permissible,",
    "start": 149.92,
    "duration": 2.576
  },
  {
    "text": "because it will lead to greater harm.",
    "start": 152.52,
    "duration": 2.68
  },
  {
    "text": "But now the idea of jihad\nhas been hijacked.",
    "start": 157.8,
    "duration": 2.496
  },
  {
    "text": "It has been perverted\nto mean violent struggle",
    "start": 160.32,
    "duration": 3.336
  },
  {
    "text": "wherever Muslims\nare undergoing difficulties,",
    "start": 163.68,
    "duration": 2.976
  },
  {
    "text": "and turned into terrorism",
    "start": 166.68,
    "duration": 1.896
  },
  {
    "text": "by fascistic Islamists like al-Qaeda,",
    "start": 168.6,
    "duration": 3.056
  },
  {
    "text": "Islamic State and others.",
    "start": 171.68,
    "duration": 1.56
  },
  {
    "text": "But I have come to understand",
    "start": 174.28,
    "duration": 1.976
  },
  {
    "text": "that true jihad\nmeans striving to the utmost",
    "start": 176.28,
    "duration": 3.936
  },
  {
    "text": "to strengthen and live\nthose qualities which God loves:",
    "start": 180.24,
    "duration": 3.36
  },
  {
    "text": "honesty, trustworthiness,",
    "start": 184.44,
    "duration": 2.336
  },
  {
    "text": "compassion, benevolence,",
    "start": 186.8,
    "duration": 2.096
  },
  {
    "text": "reliability, respect,",
    "start": 188.92,
    "duration": 1.896
  },
  {
    "text": "truthfulness --",
    "start": 190.84,
    "duration": 1.376
  },
  {
    "text": "human values that so many of us share.",
    "start": 192.24,
    "duration": 3.12
  },
  {
    "text": "I was born in Bangladesh,",
    "start": 198.36,
    "duration": 1.856
  },
  {
    "text": "but grew up mostly in England.",
    "start": 200.24,
    "duration": 1.429
  },
  {
    "text": "And I went to school here.",
    "start": 202.48,
    "duration": 1.239
  },
  {
    "text": "My father was an academic,",
    "start": 204.48,
    "duration": 2.296
  },
  {
    "text": "and we were in the UK through his work.",
    "start": 206.8,
    "duration": 2.08
  },
  {
    "text": "In 1971 we were in Bangladesh\nwhen everything changed.",
    "start": 210.36,
    "duration": 4.48
  },
  {
    "text": "The War of Independence\nimpacted upon us terribly,",
    "start": 216.24,
    "duration": 3.536
  },
  {
    "text": "pitting family against family,",
    "start": 219.8,
    "duration": 1.856
  },
  {
    "text": "neighbor against neighbor.",
    "start": 221.68,
    "duration": 1.696
  },
  {
    "text": "And at the age of 12 I experienced war,",
    "start": 223.4,
    "duration": 2.856
  },
  {
    "text": "destitution in my family,",
    "start": 226.28,
    "duration": 1.6
  },
  {
    "text": "the deaths of 22\nof my relatives in horrible ways,",
    "start": 228.72,
    "duration": 3.24
  },
  {
    "text": "as well as the murder of my elder brother.",
    "start": 232.96,
    "duration": 2.8
  },
  {
    "text": "I witnessed killing ...",
    "start": 239.04,
    "duration": 1.76
  },
  {
    "text": "animals feeding on corpses in the streets,",
    "start": 243.0,
    "duration": 2.816
  },
  {
    "text": "starvation all around me,",
    "start": 245.84,
    "duration": 1.736
  },
  {
    "text": "wanton, horrific violence --",
    "start": 247.6,
    "duration": 2.136
  },
  {
    "text": "senseless violence.",
    "start": 249.76,
    "duration": 1.2
  },
  {
    "text": "I was a young man,",
    "start": 254.28,
    "duration": 1.736
  },
  {
    "text": "teenager, fascinated by ideas.",
    "start": 256.04,
    "duration": 2.936
  },
  {
    "text": "I wanted to learn,",
    "start": 259.0,
    "duration": 1.816
  },
  {
    "text": "but I could not go to school\nfor four years.",
    "start": 260.84,
    "duration": 2.048
  },
  {
    "text": "After the War of Independence,",
    "start": 264.76,
    "duration": 1.456
  },
  {
    "text": "my father was put in prison\nfor two and a half years,",
    "start": 266.24,
    "duration": 2.48
  },
  {
    "text": "and I used to visit him\nevery week in prison,",
    "start": 269.839,
    "duration": 2.521
  },
  {
    "text": "and homeschooled myself.",
    "start": 273.12,
    "duration": 1.48
  },
  {
    "text": "My father was released in 1973",
    "start": 276.08,
    "duration": 2.56
  },
  {
    "text": "and he fled to England as a refugee,",
    "start": 279.52,
    "duration": 2.576
  },
  {
    "text": "and we soon followed him.",
    "start": 282.12,
    "duration": 1.24
  },
  {
    "text": "I was 17.",
    "start": 284.72,
    "duration": 1.656
  },
  {
    "text": "So these experiences gave me",
    "start": 286.4,
    "duration": 2.456
  },
  {
    "text": "a sharp awareness of the atrocities\nand injustices in the world.",
    "start": 288.88,
    "duration": 3.8
  },
  {
    "text": "And I had a strong desire --",
    "start": 294.32,
    "duration": 1.816
  },
  {
    "text": "a very keen, deep desire --",
    "start": 296.16,
    "duration": 2.016
  },
  {
    "text": "to right wrongs",
    "start": 298.2,
    "duration": 1.216
  },
  {
    "text": "and help the victims of oppression.",
    "start": 299.44,
    "duration": 1.667
  },
  {
    "text": "While studying at college in the UK,",
    "start": 302.6,
    "duration": 1.936
  },
  {
    "text": "I met others who showed me\nhow I could channel that desire",
    "start": 304.56,
    "duration": 5.48
  },
  {
    "text": "and help through my religion.",
    "start": 310.72,
    "duration": 1.72
  },
  {
    "text": "And I was radicalized --",
    "start": 313.72,
    "duration": 1.296
  },
  {
    "text": "enough to consider violence correct,",
    "start": 315.04,
    "duration": 3.44
  },
  {
    "text": "even a virtue under certain circumstances.",
    "start": 319.64,
    "duration": 2.36
  },
  {
    "text": "So I became involved\nin the jihad in Afghanistan.",
    "start": 324.32,
    "duration": 3.216
  },
  {
    "text": "I wanted to protect the Muslim Afghan\npopulation against the Soviet army.",
    "start": 327.56,
    "duration": 4.56
  },
  {
    "text": "And I thought that was jihad:",
    "start": 332.96,
    "duration": 2.376
  },
  {
    "text": "my sacred duty,",
    "start": 335.36,
    "duration": 1.496
  },
  {
    "text": "which would be rewarded by God.",
    "start": 336.88,
    "duration": 1.72
  },
  {
    "text": "I became a preacher.",
    "start": 343.88,
    "duration": 2.0
  },
  {
    "text": "I was one of the pioneers\nof violent jihad in the UK.",
    "start": 347.96,
    "duration": 5.096
  },
  {
    "text": "I recruited,",
    "start": 353.08,
    "duration": 1.496
  },
  {
    "text": "I raised funds, I trained.",
    "start": 354.6,
    "duration": 1.68
  },
  {
    "text": "I confused true jihad",
    "start": 357.36,
    "duration": 2.536
  },
  {
    "text": "with this perversion\nas presented by the fascist Islamists --",
    "start": 359.92,
    "duration": 4.0
  },
  {
    "text": "these people who use the idea of jihad",
    "start": 365.68,
    "duration": 3.056
  },
  {
    "text": "to justify their lust for power,\nauthority and control on earth:",
    "start": 368.76,
    "duration": 3.88
  },
  {
    "text": "a perversion perpetuated today\nby fascist Islamist groups",
    "start": 373.745,
    "duration": 4.311
  },
  {
    "text": "like al-Qaeda, Islamic State and others.",
    "start": 378.08,
    "duration": 2.88
  },
  {
    "text": "For a period of around 15 years,",
    "start": 382.44,
    "duration": 1.84
  },
  {
    "text": "I fought for short periods of time",
    "start": 385.48,
    "duration": 3.8
  },
  {
    "text": "in Kashmir and Burma,",
    "start": 390.24,
    "duration": 1.736
  },
  {
    "text": "besides Afghanistan.",
    "start": 392.0,
    "duration": 1.32
  },
  {
    "text": "Our aim was to remove the invaders,",
    "start": 397.0,
    "duration": 2.72
  },
  {
    "text": "to bring relief to the oppressed victims",
    "start": 400.76,
    "duration": 3.08
  },
  {
    "text": "and of course to establish\nan Islamic state,",
    "start": 404.88,
    "duration": 3.136
  },
  {
    "text": "a caliphate for God's rule.",
    "start": 408.04,
    "duration": 1.72
  },
  {
    "text": "And I did this openly.",
    "start": 410.72,
    "duration": 1.2
  },
  {
    "text": "I didn't break any laws.",
    "start": 413.48,
    "duration": 2.28
  },
  {
    "text": "I was proud and grateful to be British --",
    "start": 416.44,
    "duration": 3.096
  },
  {
    "text": "I still am.",
    "start": 419.56,
    "duration": 1.576
  },
  {
    "text": "And I bore no hostility\nagainst this, my country,",
    "start": 421.16,
    "duration": 3.64
  },
  {
    "text": "nor enmity towards\nthe non-Muslim citizens,",
    "start": 425.96,
    "duration": 3.536
  },
  {
    "text": "and I still don't.",
    "start": 429.52,
    "duration": 1.4
  },
  {
    "text": "During one battle in Afghanistan,",
    "start": 433.84,
    "duration": 2.376
  },
  {
    "text": "some British men and I\nformed a special bond",
    "start": 436.24,
    "duration": 2.88
  },
  {
    "text": "with a 15-year-old Afghani boy,",
    "start": 439.96,
    "duration": 2.736
  },
  {
    "text": "Abdullah,",
    "start": 442.72,
    "duration": 1.2
  },
  {
    "text": "an innocent, loving and lovable kid",
    "start": 444.84,
    "duration": 2.336
  },
  {
    "text": "who was always eager to please.",
    "start": 447.2,
    "duration": 2.04
  },
  {
    "text": "He was poor.",
    "start": 450.96,
    "duration": 1.2
  },
  {
    "text": "And boys like him\ndid menial tasks in the camp.",
    "start": 452.76,
    "duration": 2.72
  },
  {
    "text": "And he seemed happy enough,",
    "start": 456.48,
    "duration": 1.286
  },
  {
    "text": "but I couldn't help wonder --",
    "start": 458.48,
    "duration": 1.416
  },
  {
    "text": "his parents must have missed him dearly.",
    "start": 459.92,
    "duration": 1.905
  },
  {
    "text": "And they must have dreamt\nabout a better future for him.",
    "start": 463.56,
    "duration": 3.56
  },
  {
    "text": "A victim of circumstance\ncaught up in a war,",
    "start": 469.56,
    "duration": 2.816
  },
  {
    "text": "cruelly thrust upon him",
    "start": 472.4,
    "duration": 1.28
  },
  {
    "text": "by the cruel circumstances of the time.",
    "start": 474.72,
    "duration": 2.24
  },
  {
    "text": "One day I picked up this unexploded\nmortar shell in a trench,",
    "start": 480.68,
    "duration": 4.72
  },
  {
    "text": "and I had it deposited\nin a makeshift mud hut lab.",
    "start": 486.32,
    "duration": 3.8
  },
  {
    "text": "And I went out on a short,\npointless skirmish --",
    "start": 491.28,
    "duration": 2.936
  },
  {
    "text": "always pointless,",
    "start": 494.24,
    "duration": 1.2
  },
  {
    "text": "And I came back a few hours later\nto discover he was dead.",
    "start": 496.44,
    "duration": 3.44
  },
  {
    "text": "He had tried to recover\nexplosives from that shell.",
    "start": 501.16,
    "duration": 2.776
  },
  {
    "text": "It exploded, and he died a violent death,",
    "start": 503.96,
    "duration": 2.6
  },
  {
    "text": "blown to bits by the very same device\nthat had proved harmless to me.",
    "start": 507.44,
    "duration": 4.28
  },
  {
    "text": "So I started to question.",
    "start": 513.08,
    "duration": 1.52
  },
  {
    "text": "How did his death serve any purpose?",
    "start": 516.6,
    "duration": 3.72
  },
  {
    "text": "Why did he die and I lived?",
    "start": 522.28,
    "duration": 2.0
  },
  {
    "text": "I carried on.",
    "start": 525.559,
    "duration": 1.497
  },
  {
    "text": "I fought in Kashmir.",
    "start": 527.08,
    "duration": 1.616
  },
  {
    "text": "I also recruited for the Philippines,",
    "start": 528.72,
    "duration": 2.696
  },
  {
    "text": "Bosnia and Chechnya.",
    "start": 531.44,
    "duration": 1.8
  },
  {
    "text": "And the questions grew.",
    "start": 534.559,
    "duration": 1.281
  },
  {
    "text": "Later in Burma,",
    "start": 537.88,
    "duration": 1.896
  },
  {
    "text": "I came across Rohingya fighters,",
    "start": 539.8,
    "duration": 2.336
  },
  {
    "text": "who were barely teenagers,",
    "start": 542.16,
    "duration": 2.256
  },
  {
    "text": "born and brought up in the jungle,",
    "start": 544.44,
    "duration": 1.656
  },
  {
    "text": "carrying machine guns\nand grenade launchers.",
    "start": 546.12,
    "duration": 2.06
  },
  {
    "text": "I met two 13-year-olds\nwith soft manners and gentle voices.",
    "start": 552.0,
    "duration": 5.2
  },
  {
    "text": "Looking at me,",
    "start": 558.92,
    "duration": 1.216
  },
  {
    "text": "they begged me\nto take them away to England.",
    "start": 560.16,
    "duration": 2.08
  },
  {
    "text": "They simply wanted to go to school --",
    "start": 568.72,
    "duration": 1.88
  },
  {
    "text": "that was their dream.",
    "start": 571.68,
    "duration": 1.32
  },
  {
    "text": "My family --",
    "start": 576.36,
    "duration": 1.216
  },
  {
    "text": "my children of the same age --",
    "start": 577.6,
    "duration": 1.456
  },
  {
    "text": "were living at home in the UK,",
    "start": 579.08,
    "duration": 1.96
  },
  {
    "text": "going to school,",
    "start": 582.04,
    "duration": 1.296
  },
  {
    "text": "living a safe life.",
    "start": 583.36,
    "duration": 1.2
  },
  {
    "text": "And I couldn't help wonder",
    "start": 585.88,
    "duration": 1.256
  },
  {
    "text": "how much these young boys\nmust have spoken to one another",
    "start": 587.16,
    "duration": 3.456
  },
  {
    "text": "about their dreams for such a life.",
    "start": 590.64,
    "duration": 2.2
  },
  {
    "text": "Victims of circumstances:",
    "start": 594.92,
    "duration": 1.92
  },
  {
    "text": "these two young boys,",
    "start": 598.36,
    "duration": 1.28
  },
  {
    "text": "sleeping rough on the ground,\nlooking up at the stars,",
    "start": 600.32,
    "duration": 3.056
  },
  {
    "text": "cynically exploited by their leaders",
    "start": 603.4,
    "duration": 2.496
  },
  {
    "text": "for their personal lust\nfor glory and power.",
    "start": 605.92,
    "duration": 2.48
  },
  {
    "text": "I soon witnessed boys like them\nkilling one another",
    "start": 609.92,
    "duration": 3.216
  },
  {
    "text": "in conflicts between rival groups.",
    "start": 613.16,
    "duration": 2.24
  },
  {
    "text": "And it was the same everywhere ...",
    "start": 617.4,
    "duration": 2.36
  },
  {
    "text": "Afghanistan, Kashmir, Burma,",
    "start": 621.28,
    "duration": 2.496
  },
  {
    "text": "Philippines, Chechnya;",
    "start": 623.8,
    "duration": 1.48
  },
  {
    "text": "petty warlords got the young\nand vulnerable to kill one another",
    "start": 626.24,
    "duration": 4.616
  },
  {
    "text": "in the name of jihad.",
    "start": 630.88,
    "duration": 1.32
  },
  {
    "text": "Muslims against Muslims.",
    "start": 634.24,
    "duration": 1.84
  },
  {
    "text": "Not protecting anyone\nagainst invaders or occupiers;",
    "start": 637.64,
    "duration": 4.376
  },
  {
    "text": "not bringing relief to the oppressed.",
    "start": 642.04,
    "duration": 2.0
  },
  {
    "text": "Children being used,",
    "start": 646.24,
    "duration": 1.376
  },
  {
    "text": "cynically exploited;",
    "start": 647.64,
    "duration": 1.616
  },
  {
    "text": "people dying in conflicts",
    "start": 649.28,
    "duration": 1.936
  },
  {
    "text": "which I was supporting\nin the name of jihad.",
    "start": 651.24,
    "duration": 3.04
  },
  {
    "text": "And it still carries on today.",
    "start": 656.92,
    "duration": 1.64
  },
  {
    "text": "Realizing that the violent jihad",
    "start": 663.8,
    "duration": 3.616
  },
  {
    "text": "I had engaged in abroad",
    "start": 667.44,
    "duration": 4.2
  },
  {
    "text": "was so different --",
    "start": 673.44,
    "duration": 2.04
  },
  {
    "text": "such a chasm between\nwhat I had experienced",
    "start": 677.28,
    "duration": 4.736
  },
  {
    "text": "and what I thought was sacred duty --",
    "start": 682.04,
    "duration": 1.8
  },
  {
    "text": "I had to reflect\non my activities here in the UK.",
    "start": 684.64,
    "duration": 2.96
  },
  {
    "text": "I had to consider my preaching,",
    "start": 690.24,
    "duration": 2.056
  },
  {
    "text": "recruiting, fund-raising,",
    "start": 692.32,
    "duration": 1.536
  },
  {
    "text": "training,",
    "start": 693.88,
    "duration": 1.576
  },
  {
    "text": "but most importantly, radicalizing --",
    "start": 695.48,
    "duration": 2.12
  },
  {
    "text": "sending young people to fight and die",
    "start": 698.64,
    "duration": 2.216
  },
  {
    "text": "as I was doing --",
    "start": 700.88,
    "duration": 1.216
  },
  {
    "text": "all totally wrong.",
    "start": 702.12,
    "duration": 1.76
  },
  {
    "text": "So I got involved\nin violent jihad in the mid '80s,",
    "start": 707.68,
    "duration": 3.2
  },
  {
    "text": "starting with Afghanistan.",
    "start": 711.96,
    "duration": 1.48
  },
  {
    "text": "And by the time I finished\nit was in the year 2000.",
    "start": 714.6,
    "duration": 3.28
  },
  {
    "text": "I was completely immersed in it.",
    "start": 719.04,
    "duration": 1.576
  },
  {
    "text": "All around me people supported,",
    "start": 720.64,
    "duration": 1.936
  },
  {
    "text": "applauded,",
    "start": 722.6,
    "duration": 1.216
  },
  {
    "text": "even celebrated what\nwe were doing in their name.",
    "start": 723.84,
    "duration": 2.4
  },
  {
    "text": "But by the time I learned to get out,",
    "start": 728.16,
    "duration": 1.816
  },
  {
    "text": "completely disillusioned in the year 2000,",
    "start": 730.0,
    "duration": 2.616
  },
  {
    "text": "15 years had passed.",
    "start": 732.64,
    "duration": 1.68
  },
  {
    "text": "So what goes wrong?",
    "start": 737.2,
    "duration": 1.24
  },
  {
    "text": "We were so busy talking about virtue,",
    "start": 740.72,
    "duration": 2.84
  },
  {
    "text": "and we were blinded by a cause.",
    "start": 745.16,
    "duration": 3.16
  },
  {
    "text": "And we did not give ourselves a chance\nto develop a virtuous character.",
    "start": 752.24,
    "duration": 4.28
  },
  {
    "text": "We told ourselves\nwe were fighting for the oppressed,",
    "start": 757.68,
    "duration": 4.136
  },
  {
    "text": "but these were unwinnable wars.",
    "start": 761.84,
    "duration": 2.2
  },
  {
    "text": "We became the very instrument\nthrough which more deaths occurred,",
    "start": 765.72,
    "duration": 3.616
  },
  {
    "text": "complicit in causing further misery",
    "start": 769.36,
    "duration": 3.736
  },
  {
    "text": "for the selfish benefit of the cruel few.",
    "start": 773.12,
    "duration": 2.6
  },
  {
    "text": "So over time,",
    "start": 784.28,
    "duration": 1.216
  },
  {
    "text": "a very long time,",
    "start": 785.52,
    "duration": 1.2
  },
  {
    "text": "I opened my eyes.",
    "start": 788.6,
    "duration": 1.2
  },
  {
    "text": "I began to dare",
    "start": 791.96,
    "duration": 1.48
  },
  {
    "text": "to face the truth,",
    "start": 795.04,
    "duration": 1.656
  },
  {
    "text": "to think,",
    "start": 796.72,
    "duration": 1.2
  },
  {
    "text": "to face the hard questions.",
    "start": 799.36,
    "duration": 2.136
  },
  {
    "text": "I got in touch with my soul.",
    "start": 801.52,
    "duration": 2.2
  },
  {
    "text": "What have I learned?",
    "start": 814.08,
    "duration": 1.32
  },
  {
    "text": "That people who engage\nin violent jihadism,",
    "start": 816.64,
    "duration": 4.56
  },
  {
    "text": "that people who are drawn\nto these types of extremisms,",
    "start": 822.96,
    "duration": 2.6
  },
  {
    "text": "are not that different to everyone else.",
    "start": 826.6,
    "duration": 2.2
  },
  {
    "text": "But I believe such people can change.",
    "start": 829.88,
    "duration": 2.8
  },
  {
    "text": "They can regain their hearts\nand restore them",
    "start": 834.12,
    "duration": 2.856
  },
  {
    "text": "by filling them\nwith human values that heal.",
    "start": 837.0,
    "duration": 3.06
  },
  {
    "text": "When we ignore the realities,",
    "start": 847.0,
    "duration": 2.216
  },
  {
    "text": "we discover that we accept what\nwe are told without critical reflection.",
    "start": 849.24,
    "duration": 5.76
  },
  {
    "text": "And we ignore the gifts and advantages\nthat many of us would cherish",
    "start": 857.64,
    "duration": 3.776
  },
  {
    "text": "even for a single moment in their lives.",
    "start": 861.44,
    "duration": 2.28
  },
  {
    "text": "I engaged in actions\nI thought were correct.",
    "start": 868.4,
    "duration": 2.36
  },
  {
    "text": "But now I began to question\nhow I knew what I knew.",
    "start": 873.76,
    "duration": 4.0
  },
  {
    "text": "I endlessly told others\nto accept the truth,",
    "start": 879.84,
    "duration": 3.696
  },
  {
    "text": "but I failed to give doubt\nits rightful place.",
    "start": 883.56,
    "duration": 3.72
  },
  {
    "text": "This conviction that people can change\nis rooted in my experience,",
    "start": 892.92,
    "duration": 4.856
  },
  {
    "text": "my own journey.",
    "start": 897.8,
    "duration": 1.2
  },
  {
    "text": "Through wide reading,",
    "start": 900.52,
    "duration": 1.896
  },
  {
    "text": "reflecting,",
    "start": 902.44,
    "duration": 1.2
  },
  {
    "text": "contemplation, self-knowledge,",
    "start": 904.16,
    "duration": 1.896
  },
  {
    "text": "I discovered,",
    "start": 906.08,
    "duration": 1.216
  },
  {
    "text": "I realized that Islamists' world\nof us and them is false and unjust.",
    "start": 907.32,
    "duration": 5.64
  },
  {
    "text": "Through considering the uncertainties\nin all that we had asserted,",
    "start": 916.8,
    "duration": 3.68
  },
  {
    "text": "to the inviolable truths,",
    "start": 921.4,
    "duration": 1.616
  },
  {
    "text": "incontestable truths,",
    "start": 923.04,
    "duration": 1.4
  },
  {
    "text": "I developed a more nuanced understanding.",
    "start": 926.96,
    "duration": 2.88
  },
  {
    "text": "I realized that in a world crowded\nwith variation and contradiction,",
    "start": 936.48,
    "duration": 4.48
  },
  {
    "text": "foolish preachers,",
    "start": 941.92,
    "duration": 1.216
  },
  {
    "text": "only foolish preachers\nlike I used to be,",
    "start": 943.16,
    "duration": 3.016
  },
  {
    "text": "see no paradox in the myths and fictions\nthey use to assert authenticity.",
    "start": 946.2,
    "duration": 5.36
  },
  {
    "text": "So I understood the vital\nimportance of self-knowledge,",
    "start": 953.12,
    "duration": 4.536
  },
  {
    "text": "political awareness",
    "start": 957.68,
    "duration": 1.2
  },
  {
    "text": "and the necessity\nfor a deep and wide understanding",
    "start": 960.0,
    "duration": 4.656
  },
  {
    "text": "of our commitments and our actions,",
    "start": 964.68,
    "duration": 2.456
  },
  {
    "text": "how they affect others.",
    "start": 967.16,
    "duration": 1.32
  },
  {
    "text": "So my plea today to everyone,",
    "start": 970.52,
    "duration": 1.456
  },
  {
    "text": "especially those who sincerely\nbelieve in Islamist jihadism ...",
    "start": 972.0,
    "duration": 4.48
  },
  {
    "text": "refuse dogmatic authority;",
    "start": 978.48,
    "duration": 2.4
  },
  {
    "text": "let go of anger, hatred and violence;",
    "start": 982.36,
    "duration": 3.68
  },
  {
    "text": "learn to right wrongs",
    "start": 987.12,
    "duration": 1.656
  },
  {
    "text": "without even attempting to justify\ncruel, unjust and futile behavior.",
    "start": 988.8,
    "duration": 5.07
  },
  {
    "text": "Instead create a few\nbeautiful and useful things",
    "start": 996.84,
    "duration": 3.336
  },
  {
    "text": "that outlive us.",
    "start": 1000.2,
    "duration": 1.2
  },
  {
    "text": "Approach the world, life,",
    "start": 1005.2,
    "duration": 1.856
  },
  {
    "text": "with love.",
    "start": 1007.08,
    "duration": 1.2
  },
  {
    "text": "Learn to develop",
    "start": 1010.0,
    "duration": 1.216
  },
  {
    "text": "or cultivate your hearts",
    "start": 1011.24,
    "duration": 1.256
  },
  {
    "text": "to see goodness, beauty and truth\nin others and in the world.",
    "start": 1012.52,
    "duration": 3.36
  },
  {
    "text": "That way we do matter\nmore to ourselves ...",
    "start": 1017.0,
    "duration": 2.52
  },
  {
    "text": "to each other,",
    "start": 1021.24,
    "duration": 1.2
  },
  {
    "text": "to our communities",
    "start": 1023.16,
    "duration": 1.216
  },
  {
    "text": "and, for me, to God.",
    "start": 1024.4,
    "duration": 1.48
  },
  {
    "text": "This is jihad --",
    "start": 1027.0,
    "duration": 1.616
  },
  {
    "text": "my true jihad.",
    "start": 1028.64,
    "duration": 1.2
  },
  {
    "text": "Thank you.",
    "start": 1030.92,
    "duration": 1.216
  },
  {
    "text": "(Applause)",
    "start": 1032.16,
    "duration": 2.44
  }
]